        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Helicopter Data and Voice Recorder Requirement Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes it unlawful for an air carrier to operate a single or multiengine, turbine-powered helicopter with one or more passenger seats and one or more pilots without a flight data recorder and cockpit voice recorder.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
